.DT
mark_read
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
mark_read

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
mark_read -  This method marks the messages which are not in the unread array in the specified folder as being read.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void mark_read(string pname,
string fname,
int * unread)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^pname%^RESET%^ - the player name
%^BOLD%^fname%^RESET%^ - the folder name
%^BOLD%^unread%^RESET%^ - the list of messages that are still unread

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/folder_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method marks the messages which are not in the unread array
in the specified folder as being read.
.EP

